WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.461 --> 00:00:03.189
The maintain pillar entails all activities

2
00:00:03.189 --> 00:00:05.853
that occur between the moment an item is delivered

3
00:00:05.853 --> 00:00:08.323
and made operational at a facility

4
00:00:08.323 --> 00:00:10.638
and the moment when a determination has been made

5
00:00:10.638 --> 00:00:12.587
to retire that item.

6
00:00:12.587 --> 00:00:16.838
Beyond maintenance and repair operations, M and RO,

7
00:00:16.838 --> 00:00:19.581
and parts, supplies, and spares management,

8
00:00:19.581 --> 00:00:21.597
the maintain function also addresses

9
00:00:21.597 --> 00:00:24.534
important topics like service level monitoring

10
00:00:24.534 --> 00:00:26.579
and quality assurance and control.

